ascend_skill.desc:
Inflict Radiation on foes with elemental ailments for 2 turns.
Radiation: Increase damage taken by 15%. Radiation counts as an elemental ailment.
ascend_skill.name: Veteran Technique

ascend_skill.desc: When foes with Radiation are also inflicted with Burn, Shock, Freeze, or Windswept, increase corresponding Fire, Electric, Ice, or Wind damage taken by 15%.
ascend_skill.name: Grandmotherly Care

ascend_skill.desc: When an ally inflicts an elemental ailment, increase Chizuko's ailment accuracy by 10% for 2 turns. Stacks up to 3 times.
ascend_skill.name: From Now On

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Diving Ray and Blunt Edge by 2.
ascend_skill.name: Jazz Session

ascend_skill.desc: Highlight Enhanced: Increase foes' Nuclear damage taken by 35.2% for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: The Older, the Wiser

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Bullseye Bomber and Thief Tactics by 2.
ascend_skill.name: Long-time Player

ascend_skill.desc:
When an ally attacks a foe with Radiation, activate the following effects based on the number of unique elemental ailments on the foe. (Effects will stack.)
1 or more: Increase Attack by 10%.
2 or more: Increase Nuclear damage by 10%.
3 or more: Increase pierce rate by 8%.
ascend_skill.name: Unending

highlight_skill.desc: Deal Nuclear damage to 1 foe equal to 324.5%/357.8%/337.8%/371.1% of Attack. Has a 75% chance to inflict 2 random elemental ailments that the foe does not already have.
highlight_skill.name: Highlight

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Nuclear damage to 1 foe equal to 170.8%/188.3%/177.8%/195.3% of Attack.
For 2 turns, decrease the target's Defense by 22.5% of Chizuko's ailment accuracy (up to 37.3%/37.3%/38.8%/38.8%) and inflict a random elemental ailment that the target does not already have.
normal_skill.name: Diving Ray

normal_skill.desc: Deal Nuclear damage to all foes equal to 91.5%/100.9%/95.2%/104.6% of Attack. Has a 40% chance to inflict a random elemental ailment that the foe does not already have.
normal_skill.name: Blunt Edge

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Nuclear damage to 1 foe equal to 195.2%/215.2%/203.2%/223.2% of Attack.
Increase the target's damage taken by 11.3% of Chizuko's ailment accuracy (up to 18.7%/20.7%/19.5%/21.4%) for 2 turns, based on the number of unique elemental ailments they have.
normal_skill.name: Bullseye Bomber

passive_skill.desc: Increase Nuclear damage taken by foes with Radiation by 15.0%. Lasts for 2 turns.
passive_skill.name: Eagle Eye

passive_skill.desc: Increase Attack by 45.0% of ailment accuracy.
passive_skill.name: Perfect Timing
